NAME
	strlen - give the length of a string

SYNOPSIS
	int strlen(int|string str, void|int ignore_color)

OPTIONS 
	str          - the string to get the length of
                       if an integer is passed 0 is returned
	ignore_color - if true ansi color codes are ignored
                       during calculation of string length

DESCRIPTION
	Gives the length of a string in number of characters.


